1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乡村明星 Jelly Roll 本周向美国国会提出反芬太尼立法的动情呼吁。</p><p>这位真名杰森·德福德的音乐家克服了自己的毒瘾，并向国会表示，虽然他“曾经是问题的一部分”，但现在他希望成为“解决方案的一部分”，并敦促美国立法者通过一项抗芬太尼法案。法律。</p><p>官员们表示，芬太尼在美国每天导致近 200 人死亡，是 45 岁以下美国成年人死亡的主要原因（来自<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2024/jan/13/jelly-roll-anti-fentanyl-bill-congress" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报</em>》）。</a></p><p>这种药物最近经常出现在新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coolio-cause-of-death-accidental-fentanyl-overdose-3427107">例如说唱歌手库里奥去年因意外服用芬太尼过量而死亡</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/priscilla-presley">普雷斯利的</a>儿子纳瓦罗内·加里波第<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/priscilla-presleys-son-navarone-garibaldi-speaks-out-on-fentanyl-addiction-my-mum-helped-me-i-was-useless-3567324">最近也公开了他“难以忍受”的芬太尼成瘾，他说这几乎要了他的命，并称赞他的母亲帮助他戒毒。</a></p><p>德福德在<a href="https://www.c-span.org/video/?c5101539/music-artist-jelly-roll-appeals-congress-action-fentanyl-crisis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参议院银行、住房和城市事务委员会</a>发表讲话时说：“我参加过的葬礼比我愿意与大家分享的还要多……我可以坐在这里为我所携带的人们的棺材哭泣几天。深深地爱着，深深地爱在我的灵魂里。好人，不仅仅是吸毒者。叔叔、朋友、表兄弟姐妹、普通人。” </p><figure id="attachment_3570566" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3570566" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3570566" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3570566" class="wp-caption-text">乡村音乐家 Jelly Roll 在参议院听证会上就阻止芬太尼的流通作证 — 图片来源：Kent Nishimura/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说道：“我让我的社区崩溃了。我伤害了人。我是一个没有受过教育的人，在厨房里用我一无所知的药物扮演化学家，就像这些毒贩现在所做的那样，他们将市场上的每种药物与芬太尼混合，然后杀死我们所爱的人。</p><p> “……我建议我们站起来，尽快采取更多行动。”</p><p>目前，国会正在考虑是否批准《芬太尼根除和麻醉品威慑芬太尼法案》，该法案也被称为“抵御芬太尼法案”。</p><p>该法案提议实施制裁和反洗钱战略，以阻止阿片类药物的流动。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/country-artist-jelly-roll-makes-plea-for-anti-fentanyl-legislation-3570564">乡村艺术家 Jelly Roll 呼吁反芬太尼立法的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
