w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Neve-Campbell-on-returning-to-Scream-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Neve-Campbell-on-returning-to-Scream-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Neve-Campbell-on-returning-to-Scream-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>最近有消息称，几名演员和导演离开了即将上映的这部长期上映的电影，内夫·坎贝尔公开了<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/scream">《惊声尖叫》</a></em>系列电影的情况。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/scream-6-review-ghostface-jenna-ortega-3409588">《惊声尖叫 VI》评论：穿越不夜城的噩梦般的惊险之旅</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在去年 12 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-director-christopher-landon-quits-project-3562999"><em>《惊声尖叫 7</em> 》的导演克里斯托弗·兰登就证实他已辞去该项目的工作。</a>这位<em>《忌日快乐》</em>导演被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-in-the-works-with-happy-death-day-director-3477470">宣布将于八月执导第七部</a>，这将标志着他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/scream"><em>《惊声尖叫》</em></a>系列中的处女作。他本应接替马特·贝蒂内利-奥尔平和泰勒·吉列的职位，后者执导了 2022 年的<em>《惊声尖叫 5》</em>和今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/scream-vi"><em>《惊声尖叫 6》</em></a> ，并准备担任下一部电影的执行制片人。</p><p> “我想现在是宣布我<em>7 周前正式退出 Scream 的</em>最佳时机，”兰登去年 12 月在 X（前身为 Twitter）上说道。 “这会让一些人失望，也让另一些人高兴。这是一份梦想的工作，却变成了一场噩梦。我为所有参与其中的人感到心碎。每个人。但现在是时候继续前进了。”</p><p>紧接着珍娜·奥尔特加 (Jenna Ortega) 和梅丽莎·巴雷拉 (Melissa Barrera) 高调离职。</p><p>奥尔特加决定不再继续扮演塔拉·卡彭特这个角色，因为她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jenna-ortega-will-not-be-returning-to-the-scream-franchise-3546990">仍在参与其他项目</a>。与此同时，巴雷拉因在社交媒体上分享亲巴勒斯坦的帖子而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-vow-to-boycott-scream-vii-after-melissa-barrera-is-dropped-over-israel-hamas-war-post-3546483">被影片开除</a>——这导致<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-vow-to-boycott-scream-vii-after-melissa-barrera-is-dropped-over-israel-hamas-war-post-3546483">粉丝发誓抵制<em>《惊声尖叫VII》。</em></a></p><p>坎贝尔此前曾在<em>《惊声尖叫 6》</em>上映期间因片酬纠纷而退出该剧，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-stars-support-neve-campbell-after-she-exits-scream-6-over-pay-dispute-3243767">她的许多搭档都支持她的决定</a>。然而，去年 11 月有报道称，作为“创意改革”的一部分<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-vii-reportedly-eyeing-neve-campbells-return-in-creative-overhaul-3548576">，Spyglass 一直试图让她回归</a><em>《惊声尖叫 7》</em> ，并提出了让<em>《惊声尖叫 3》</em>的对手帕特里克·德姆西也回归的可能性。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C2D-020Rj2Y/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551